title: Black Fridays - Fallen Master Tapes - China - Part 5
description: For this installment of Black Fridays, we have part 5 of a Fallen master tape from a trip to China. Riders in this video are Tom Asta, Tommy Sandoval, Brian 'Slash' Hansen, James Hardy and Jamie Thomas.
